ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCanadian Nuclear Safety Commission - Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada ** Collective Agreement **
PrecisOrder approving the ENTRY by the Canadian Nuclear Safety Commission into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada that covers all employees in the NUCLEAR REGULATORY GROUP bargaining unit for the period beginning on April 1, 2018 and ending on March 31, 2022.
